        "innerText": "129"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Puññāpuññavipākā hi, kāme dasa ca pañca ca hi"
      },
      " saccaṃ ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "kāme"
      },
      " kāmāvacare kusalākusalavipākā dasa pañca ca kiriyā tisso iti sabbe ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "aṭṭhārasa"
      },
      " cittuppādā ahetukā."
    ],
    "innerText": "129.Puññāpuññavipākā hi, kāme dasa ca pañca ca hi saccaṃ kāme kāmāvacare kusalākusalavipākā dasa pañca ca kiriyā tisso iti sabbe aṭṭhārasa cittuppādā ahetukā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "130"
      },
      ". Ahetukato cittuppādato ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "sesā"
      },
      " ekasattati cittuppādā ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "sahetukāti"
      },
      " sahetukā nāmāti mahesinā ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "tādinā"
      },
      " aviparītasabhāvena ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "hetuvādinā"
      },
      " paccayavādinā niddiṭṭhā."
    ],
    "innerText": "130. Ahetukato cittuppādato sesā ekasattati cittuppādā sahetukāti sahetukā nāmāti mahesinā tādinā aviparītasabhāvena hetuvādinā paccayavādinā niddiṭṭhā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "131"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Savatthukāvatthukato"
      },
      " savatthukaavatthukavasena tathā ubhayavasena savatthukavasena, avatthukavasena ca sabbaṃ vuttappakārena ca mānasaṃ tividhaṃ hoti."
    ],
    "innerText": "131.Savatthukāvatthukato savatthukaavatthukavasena tathā ubhayavasena savatthukavasena, avatthukavasena ca sabbaṃ vuttappakārena ca mānasaṃ tividhaṃ hoti."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "132-4"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Sabbo kāmavipāko ca, rūpe pañcadasāpi ca"
      },
      " cittuppādā ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "ādimaggo"
      },
      " paṭhamamaggo hasituppādo manodhātukiriyāpi ca domanassadvayañcāpi tecattālīsa mānasā ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "vinā vatthuṃ"
      },
      " vatthuṃ vajjetvā na uppajjanti, ekantena savatthukā nāma. Arūpāvacaravipākā ca ekantena ",
      " avatthukā, mayā vuttato cittuppādato ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "sesāni"
      },
      " dvecattālīsa cittāni ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "ubhayathā"
      },
      " savatthukāvatthukavasena siyuṃ."
    ],
    "innerText": "132-4.Sabbo kāmavipāko ca, rūpe pañcadasāpi ca cittuppādā ādimaggo paṭhamamaggo hasituppādo manodhātukiriyāpi ca domanassadvayañcāpi tecattālīsa mānasā vinā vatthuṃ vatthuṃ vajjetvā na uppajjanti, ekantena savatthukā nāma. Arūpāvacaravipākā ca ekantena avatthukā, mayā vuttato cittuppādato sesāni dvecattālīsa cittāni ubhayathā savatthukāvatthukavasena siyuṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "135"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Ekekārammaṇaṃ cittaṃ, pañcārammaṇameva ca"
      },
      " cittaṃ chaḷārammaṇakañceti ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "evaṃ"
      },
      " iminā mayā vuttappakārenāpi tividhaṃ cittaṃ siyā."
    ],
    "innerText": "135.Ekekārammaṇaṃ cittaṃ, pañcārammaṇameva ca cittaṃ chaḷārammaṇakañceti evaṃ iminā mayā vuttappakārenāpi tividhaṃ cittaṃ siyā."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "136-8"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Viññāṇāni ca dve pañca, aṭṭha lokuttarāni ca"
      },
      " abhiññāmānasaṃ ṭhapetvā sabbaṃ mahaggatañcevāti ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "tecattālīsa"
      },
      " cittuppādā pana ekekārammaṇā viññeyyā dhīrena. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Tattha"
      },
      " citte manodhātuttayaṃ pañcārammaṇaṃ īritaṃ bhagavatā. Mayā vuttacittato ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "sesāni tecattālīsa"
      },
      " cittāni chaḷārammaṇikāni matāni satthunā, tathā evaṃ cittaṃ kusalākusalādito tividhaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Ādi"
      },
      "-saddena abyākataṃ gahetabbaṃ."
    ],
    "innerText": "136-8.Viññāṇāni ca dve pañca, aṭṭha lokuttarāni ca abhiññāmānasaṃ ṭhapetvā sabbaṃ mahaggatañcevāti tecattālīsa cittuppādā pana ekekārammaṇā viññeyyā dhīrena. Tattha citte manodhātuttayaṃ pañcārammaṇaṃ īritaṃ bhagavatā. Mayā vuttacittato sesāni tecattālīsa cittāni chaḷārammaṇikāni matāni satthunā, tathā evaṃ cittaṃ kusalākusalādito tividhaṃ. Ādi-saddena abyākataṃ gahetabbaṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
