        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "139"
      },
      ". Ahetukaṃ cittaṃ ekahetukañca cittaṃ dvihetukañca cittaṃ tihetukañca cittanti ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "evaṃ"
      },
      " iminā pakārena cittaṃ catubbidhaṃ vibhāvinā viññātabbaṃ."
    ],
    "innerText": "139. Ahetukaṃ cittaṃ ekahetukañca cittaṃ dvihetukañca cittaṃ tihetukañca cittanti evaṃ iminā pakārena cittaṃ catubbidhaṃ vibhāvinā viññātabbaṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "140-2"
      },
      ". Heṭṭhā mayāpi niddiṭṭhā ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "aṭṭhārasa"
      },
      " cittuppādā ahetukā, ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "vicikicchuddhaccasaṃyuttaṃ"
      },
      " cittaṃ ekahetukaṃ evaṃ udīritaṃ bhagavatā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Kāme"
      },
      " kāmāvacare ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "puññavipākakriyato"
      },
      " kusalavasena ca vipākavasena ca kiriyāvasena ca ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "dvādasadhā"
      },
      " cittuppādā akusalā ca dasadhā cāti bāvīsati cittuppādā duhetukā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Kāme"
      },
      " kāmāvacare ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "puññavipākakriyato"
      },
      " puññavasena ca vipākavasena ca kiriyāvasena ca ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "dvādasadhā"
      },
      " cittuppādā. Sabbaṃ mahaggatañceva ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "appamāṇaṃ"
      },
      " lokuttaracittañca tihetukaṃ."
    ],
    "innerText": "140-2. Heṭṭhā mayāpi niddiṭṭhā aṭṭhārasa cittuppādā ahetukā, vicikicchuddhaccasaṃyuttaṃ cittaṃ ekahetukaṃ evaṃ udīritaṃ bhagavatā. Kāme kāmāvacare puññavipākakriyato kusalavasena ca vipākavasena ca kiriyāvasena ca dvādasadhā cittuppādā akusalā ca dasadhā cāti bāvīsati cittuppādā duhetukā. Kāme kāmāvacare puññavipākakriyato puññavasena ca vipākavasena ca kiriyāvasena ca dvādasadhā cittuppādā. Sabbaṃ mahaggatañceva appamāṇaṃ lokuttaracittañca tihetukaṃ."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "143-50"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Rūpīriyāpathaviññatti-janakājanakādito"
      },
      "ti rūpairiyāpathaviññattijanakavasena rūpairiyāpathajanakavasena ca rūpajanakavasena ca tikiccājanakavasena cātiādīhi pakārehi sabbaṃ cittaṃ catubbidhaṃ hoti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Tattha"
      },
      " tasmiṃ citte dvādasākusalā, kāmadhātuyā kusalā, tathā kāme dasa kiriyā, abhiññāmānasaṃ dvayaṃ, ime bāttiṃsa mānasā rūpāni samuṭṭhāpenti, iriyāpathaṃ kappenti, viññattiṃ janayanti. Kusalā mahaggatamānasā kiriyā ca mahaggatamānasā, ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "aṭṭha"
      },
      " anāsavacittāni, chabbīsati ca mānasā rūpāni samuṭṭhāpenti, iriyāpathaṃ ",
      " kappenti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Copanaṃ na pāpenti"
      },
      " viññattiṃ na janayantīti attho. Ime cittuppādā dukiccaniyatā ",
      ", dasa viññāṇe ṭhapetvā dvīsu bhūmīsu ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "vipākā"
      },
      " manodhātudvayasantīraṇattayamahāvipākarūpavipākānaṃ vasena aṭṭhārasa pākā manodhātu kiriyā cevāti ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "imāni ekūnavīsati"
      },
      " cittāni rūpāni samuṭṭhāpenti, itaradvayaṃ na karonti, ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "puna dvepañcaviññāṇā"
      },
      " paṭhamaṃ ‘‘dasa viññāṇe’’ti vuttattā ‘‘punā’’ti vuttā. Arūpīsu vipākā ca ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "sabbesaṃ"
      },
      " sattānaṃ paṭisandhicittañca arahato cuticittañca ime soḷasa mānasā tikiccāni na karonti."
    ],
    "innerText": "143-50.Rūpīriyāpathaviññatti-janakājanakāditoti rūpairiyāpathaviññattijanakavasena rūpairiyāpathajanakavasena ca rūpajanakavasena ca tikiccājanakavasena cātiādīhi pakārehi sabbaṃ cittaṃ catubbidhaṃ hoti. Tattha tasmiṃ citte dvādasākusalā, kāmadhātuyā kusalā, tathā kāme dasa kiriyā, abhiññāmānasaṃ dvayaṃ, ime bāttiṃsa mānasā rūpāni samuṭṭhāpenti, iriyāpathaṃ kappenti, viññattiṃ janayanti. Kusalā mahaggatamānasā kiriyā ca mahaggatamānasā, aṭṭha anāsavacittāni, chabbīsati ca mānasā rūpāni samuṭṭhāpenti, iriyāpathaṃ kappenti. Copanaṃ na pāpenti viññattiṃ na janayantīti attho. Ime cittuppādā dukiccaniyatā , dasa viññāṇe ṭhapetvā dvīsu bhūmīsu vipākā manodhātudvayasantīraṇattayamahāvipākarūpavipākānaṃ vasena aṭṭhārasa pākā manodhātu kiriyā cevāti imāni ekūnavīsati cittāni rūpāni samuṭṭhāpenti, itaradvayaṃ na karonti, puna dvepañcaviññāṇā paṭhamaṃ ‘‘dasa viññāṇe’’ti vuttattā ‘‘punā’’ti vuttā. Arūpīsu vipākā ca sabbesaṃ sattānaṃ paṭisandhicittañca arahato cuticittañca ime soḷasa mānasā tikiccāni na karonti."
  },
